org.springframework.web.reactive.result.method.annotation

类 AbstractMessageReaderArgumentResolver

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.springframework.web.reactive.result.method.annotation.AbstractMessageReaderArgumentResolver
  • 直接已知子类:
    HttpEntityArgumentResolver, RequestBodyArgumentResolver

    public abstract class AbstractMessageReaderArgumentResolver
extends Object
    Abstract base class for argument resolvers that resolve method arguments by reading the request body with an HttpMessageReader.

    Applies validation if the method argument is annotated with @javax.validation.Valid or Validated. Validation failure results in an ServerWebInputException.

    从以下版本开始:
    5.0
    作者:
    Rossen Stoyanchev
